app_name: Groups Control Groups Voice Recording and Karaoke Apps WinSmart Karaoke
app_description: WinSmart Karaoke provides all available karaoke songs. You can search for songs by entering text or by voice. You love a certain song add it to the favorites list to have a song collection for you. The application provides you with a simple interface to connect to your transmitter. The application is a great choice to enjoy happy moments with family and friends ..
